{"tid":2496001,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖][慎入] 前員工踢爆黑心偽黃奶茶舖","createTime":"2021-04-19T13:53:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T14:24:27.000Z","uid":384614,"like":45,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"e5a4d96c011aab31fb9da1fe68662b94751feade","tid":2496001,"uid":384614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:53:47.000Z","msg":"本人係太子、油麻地茶樂前員工。<br />\n<br />\n去到一月份左右舖頭有老鼠，係兩間分店都有！！！老鼠咬爛啲真空珍珠，同事好心提佢但老闆娘一於當睇唔到，要求我哋繼續煲，話只係唔小心刮爛包裝。<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVp46xLnnPGXD6VXNefsHYkDLVYxxx6VHYYCCLAznvMTG?filename=7CV506g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7CV506g.jpg&h=fe6f2db9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYmCJf236ZNHhzQFCUYiQru4f6zqdgaUGRqJ2enb5ofQv?filename=n6vBojD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn6vBojD.jpg&h=b4414069&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbegkE7aRtzTWBFewjRqbjVu7Hanwa7kGBQspbSi8423v?filename=1GHDBEH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1GHDBEH.jpg&h=07556507&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZ9yegeTabafibpFZeT7FSQ4XzdQ9i6vsD65poo5jjv36?filename=N69bcc5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN69bcc5.jpg&h=6b2b583c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPQy9KtNwjMB3coCJQWqJ88XnpYSzr3AwWr6R4suLjz9F?filename=Lyc4xda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLyc4xda.jpg&h=3cbc97ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmV27r822aSqGQrt6yZANmxhJSJcwyRSjtFkDR3Am1r4t8?filename=WkJn3jT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWkJn3jT.jpg&h=bd519dea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmec5kUJcmESe1fVSTc7hJx6myvcxNwXS3BWNDdC9HAKHK?filename=YepniTf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYepniTf.jpg&h=fd1f437e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmc5emst3GsoZSES1nxnQryhHYGgkDhhVeSdhSaTuTs7jq?filename=JaAYBEW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJaAYBEW.jpg&h=ecc9e95d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後每次老闆娘臨返屋企前會叫同事煮一煲新嘅、冇比老鼠咬過嘅珍珠，for佢帶返屋企比佢啲仔女飲。<br />\n<br />\n由老鼠事件開始，我就默默留意舖頭嘅用料、食材。<br />\n唔睇仲好一睇就出事！除咗每日要嘅珍珠、芋圓，差唔多全部都過期！！！！！<br />\n最嚴重更加係過期足足兩年，有同事好心同老闆娘講，佢竟然以生產商印錯日期為由，話材料冇過期，甚至要求同事試食。<br />\n所以我開始默默影低佢嘅過期嘢！<br />\n（今日收到風有25仔爆咗比老闆娘聽，而佢dum咗部分冇得met走最佳食用日期嘅食材，但同時保留部分可以met走最佳食用日期嘅食材照用）<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPieeMNK36zzATNzitgYNTjnyiuCxZ3Gk2uRt2F6MAVzF?filename=QpS4xdo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQpS4xdo.jpg&h=6bc2f506&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaLoKtiipdCRQJwfknYe3A5bRTJ2f8yURxEru3661bEK4?filename=d85d9Z4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd85d9Z4.jpg&h=832f119b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZRU2iNQhiF1encK9zSXXHp3dTabyTjsoSsmBKqJTm8Ma?filename=hq6dqyr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhq6dqyr.jpg&h=3dbffb5d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQqXBAACbtaDSKtMSwqMCNkus25r9gibgragoJKKc6Hon?filename=7GgH3j6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7GgH3j6.jpg&h=6231d889&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbTDBi4n1DXRV5qQQHNN8sphUNJfdMBbQkKKyA28RQngi?filename=HiT7uZ8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHiT7uZ8.jpg&h=31207fb9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYaXeZgsq8VZcemFtQjd8sYVjWLCsdQQK4CHEcXATRipx?filename=AzbH3kd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAzbH3kd.png&h=d58f32dd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUiyMnJa4xL9xUUhQwcuFyNhA29jtyJ5WEZTSNFzWPKLz?filename=hiofDTz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhiofDTz.jpg&h=0484608b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmf12DvrJYdLUKGKCoyMqzRera9senVeJfGEq7esa5C4M1?filename=18szUrV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F18szUrV.jpg&h=63652a35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n十月份開始係茶樂返工，一開始上網睇過話係黃店，仲係油麻地貼出炒咗個藍屍嘅公告出嚟。<br />\n結果返工開始就知道，老細同老闆娘都係大陸人，係大陸開連鎖藥店(老闆娘自爆+google過老細個名)，但就偽黃食兩家茶飯。<br />\n佢哋一開始有4間分店，依家執到得返兩間，行過路過記得唔好幫襯，話埋比身邊朋友同屋企人知！<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmX1RiYXtFjRcpAQyUGNssSPZnU8gTY1x8oqhAv4HkWCzq?filename=jqXzUsr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjqXzUsr.png&h=4f374e01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f52fd20e91e09a37f502dc0751719eaa79ae9f8f","tid":2496001,"uid":168366,"like":21,"dislike":4,"score":17,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:54:08.000Z","msg":"好可愛<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPQy9KtNwjMB3coCJQWqJ88XnpYSzr3AwWr6R4suLjz9F?filename=Lyc4xda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLyc4xda.jpg&h=3cbc97ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40faa40a1b8fadab6dea078b0b44d01ff5d6aed1","tid":2496001,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f52fd20e91e09a37f502dc0751719eaa79ae9f8f","tid":2496001,"uid":168366,"like":21,"dislike":4,"score":17,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:54:08.000Z","msg":"好可愛<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lyc4xda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLyc4xda.jpg&h=3cbc97ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:56:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7066938aa110a08117569bc52eeb4a343363e46f","tid":2496001,"uid":179967,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:58:29.000Z","msg":"我理得你真黃假黃<br />\n你老母咁大隻老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16d9486c0debba20d611a41b7fa726553e787c5","tid":2